To run the offloading code

compile parboil.c with
clang -fopenmp -fopenmp-targets=nvptx64-nvidia-cuda  parboil.c -c

link and run main file
clang -fopenmp -fopenmp-targets=nvptx64-nvidia-cuda stencil_profile.c parboil.o -o runnable -lm

to run the file , data set inside zip file
./runnable -i path/512x512x64x100.bin nx ny nz t
nx: the grid size x
ny: the grid size y
nz: the grid size z
t: the iteration time

eg:512 512 64 200
changing iteration time can result better GPU performance compared to CPU
my threshold = 200
